      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Conferences\" title=\"Conferences\">Conferences</a> * Computer and Games 2008</b>\n</p><p><b><a href=\"/CG_2006\" title=\"CG 2006\">&lt; Prev</a> <a href=\"/CG_2010\" title=\"CG 2010\">Next &gt;</a></b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"http://www.geocities.jp/hideki_katoh/13days/5th_day/slides/DSCF3084.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/Bejing2008ICGAVenue.jpg/300px-Bejing2008ICGAVenue.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/9/9f/Bejing2008ICGAVenue.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Bejing2008ICGAVenue.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The venue of the Championships and <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Conference</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p>The <b>Sixth International Conference on Computers and Games</b> was held from September 29 to October 1, <a href=\"/Timeline#2008\" title=\"Timeline\">2008</a> at Beijing Golden Century Golf Club, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_township-level_divisions_of_Beijing#Fangshan_District\">Qinglonghu Township</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fangshan_District\">Fangshan District</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beijing\">Beijing</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/China\">China</a>, in conjunction with the <a href=\"/13th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"13th Computer Olympiad\">13th Computer Olympiad</a> and the <a href=\"/WCCC_2008\" title=\"WCCC 2008\">16th World Computer Chess Championship</a> . \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Proceedings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Proceedings</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Lectures\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Lectures</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Proceedings\">Proceedings</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CG_2008&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Proceedings\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a>, <a href=\"/Xinhe_Xu\" title=\"Xinhe Xu\">Xinhe Xu</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Zongmin_Ma&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Zongmin Ma (page does not exist)\">Zongmin Ma</a>, <a href=\"/Mark_Winands\" title=\"Mark Winands\">Mark Winands</a> (eds.)</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/book/10.1007%2F978-3-540-87608-3\">Computers and Games</a> </dd>\n<dd> 6th International Conference, CG 2008</dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beijing\">Beijing</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/China\">China</a>, September 29 - October 1, 2008</dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lecture_Notes_in_Computer_Science\">Lecture Notes in Computer Science</a>, Volume 5131, 2008</dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a> Berlin / Heidelberg</dd>\n<dd> ISBN 978-3-540-87607-6 </dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Lectures\">Lectures</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CG_2008&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Lectures\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Maarten_Schadd&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Maarten Schadd (page does not exist)\">Maarten Schadd</a>, <a href=\"/Mark_Winands\" title=\"Mark Winands\">Mark Winands</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a>, <a href=\"/Guillaume_Chaslot\" title=\"Guillaume Chaslot\">Guillaume Chaslot</a>, <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_1\">Single-Player Monte-Carlo Tree Search</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.personeel.unimaas.nl/Maarten-Schadd/Papers/2008SameGameCG.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Richard_J._Lorentz\" title=\"Richard J. Lorentz\">Richard J. Lorentz</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_2\">Amazons Discover Monte-Carlo</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mark_Winands\" title=\"Mark Winands\">Mark Winands</a>, <a href=\"/Yngvi_Bj%C3%B6rnsson\" title=\"Yngvi Björnsson\">Yngvi Björnsson</a>, <a href=\"/Jahn-Takeshi_Saito\" title=\"Jahn-Takeshi Saito\">Jahn-Takeshi Saito</a>  (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_3\">Monte-Carlo Tree Search Solver</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ru.is/faculty/yngvi/pdf/WinandsBS08.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Nathan_Sturtevant\" title=\"Nathan Sturtevant\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_4\">An Analysis of UCT in Multi-player Games</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tristan_Cazenave\" title=\"Tristan Cazenave\">Tristan Cazenave</a>  (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_5\">Multi-player Go</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Guillaume_Chaslot\" title=\"Guillaume Chaslot\">Guillaume Chaslot</a>, <a href=\"/Mark_Winands\" title=\"Mark Winands\">Mark Winands</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_6\">Parallel Monte-Carlo Tree Search</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dke.maastrichtuniversity.nl/m.winands/documents/multithreadedMCTS2.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tristan_Cazenave\" title=\"Tristan Cazenave\">Tristan Cazenave</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Nicolas_Jouandeau&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Nicolas Jouandeau (page does not exist)\">Nicolas Jouandeau</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_7\">A Parallel Monte-Carlo Tree Search Algorithm</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lamsade.dauphine.fr/%7Ecazenave/papers/parallelMCTS.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ling_Zhao&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ling Zhao (page does not exist)\">Ling Zhao</a>, <a href=\"/Martin_M%C3%BCller\" title=\"Martin Müller\">Martin Müller</a>  (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_8\">Using Artificial Boundaries in the Game of Go</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Keh-Hsun_Chen\" title=\"Keh-Hsun Chen\">Ken Chen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Dawei_Du&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Dawei Du (page does not exist)\">Dawei Du</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Peigang_Zhang&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Peigang Zhang (page does not exist)\">Peigang Zhang</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_9\">A Fast Indexing Method for Monte-Carlo Go</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Xiaozhen_Niu&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Xiaozhen Niu (page does not exist)\">Xiaozhen Niu</a>, <a href=\"/Martin_M%C3%BCller\" title=\"Martin Müller\">Martin Müller</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_10\">An Improved Safety Solver in Go Using Partial Regions</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/R%C3%A9mi_Coulom\" title=\"Rémi Coulom\">Rémi Coulom</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_11\">Whole-History Rating: A Bayesian Rating System for Players of Time-Varying Strength</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Zhiqing_Liu&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Zhiqing Liu (page does not exist)\">Zhiqing Liu</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Qing_Dou&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Qing Dou (page does not exist)\">Qing Dou</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Benjie_Lu&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Benjie Lu (page does not exist)\">Benjie Lu</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_12\">Frequency Distribution of Contextual Patterns in the Game of Go</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Kazuki_Yoshizoe&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Kazuki Yoshizoe (page does not exist)\">Kazuki Yoshizoe</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_13\">A New Proof-Number Calculation Technique for Proof-Number Search</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Akihiro_Kishimoto\" title=\"Akihiro Kishimoto\">Akihiro Kishimoto</a>, <a href=\"/Martin_M%C3%BCller\" title=\"Martin Müller\">Martin Müller</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_14\">About the Completeness of Depth-First Proof-Number Search</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Toru_Ueda&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Toru Ueda (page does not exist)\">Toru Ueda</a>, <a href=\"/Tsuyoshi_Hashimoto\" title=\"Tsuyoshi Hashimoto\">Tsuyoshi Hashimoto</a>, <a href=\"/Junichi_Hashimoto\" title=\"Junichi Hashimoto\">Junichi Hashimoto</a>, <a href=\"/Hiroyuki_Iida\" title=\"Hiroyuki Iida\">Hiroyuki Iida</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_15\">Weak Proof-Number Search</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Reijer_Grimbergen\" title=\"Reijer Grimbergen\">Reijer Grimbergen</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_16\">Cognitive Modeling of Knowledge-Guided Information Acquisition in Games</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Pangfeng_Liu\" title=\"Pangfeng Liu\">Pangfeng Liu</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_17\">Knowledge Inferencing on Chinese Chess Endgames</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Matej_Guid\" title=\"Matej Guid\">Matej Guid</a>, <a href=\"/Martin_Mo%C5%BEina\" title=\"Martin Možina\">Martin Možina</a>, <a href=\"/Jana_Krivec\" title=\"Jana Krivec\">Jana Krivec</a>, <a href=\"/Aleksander_Sadikov\" title=\"Aleksander Sadikov\">Aleksander Sadikov</a>, <a href=\"/Ivan_Bratko\" title=\"Ivan Bratko\">Ivan Bratko</a>  (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_18\">Learning Positional Features for Annotating Chess Games: A Case Study</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ailab.si/matej/doc/Learning_Positional_Features-Case_Study.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Eli_David\" title=\"Eli David\">Omid David</a>, <a href=\"/Nathan_S._Netanyahu\" title=\"Nathan S. Netanyahu\">Nathan S. Netanyahu</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_19\">Extended Null-Move Reductions</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.oedavid.com/pubs/nmr.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/J%C3%B3nhei%C3%B0ur_%C3%8Dsleifsd%C3%B3ttir\" title=\"Jónheiður Ísleifsdóttir\">Jónheiður Ísleifsdóttir</a>, <a href=\"/Yngvi_Bj%C3%B6rnsson\" title=\"Yngvi Björnsson\">Yngvi Björnsson</a>. (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_20\">GTQ: A Language and Tool for Game-Tree Analysis</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ru.is/faculty/yngvi/pdf/IsleifsdottirB08.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Philip_Henderson&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Philip Henderson (page does not exist)\">Philip Henderson</a>, <a href=\"/Ryan_Hayward\" title=\"Ryan Hayward\">Ryan Hayward</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_21\">Probing the 4-3-2 Edge Template in Hex</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~hayward/papers/probe432.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Alessandro_Cincotti&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Alessandro Cincotti (page does not exist)\">Alessandro Cincotti</a>, <a href=\"/Hiroyuki_Iida\" title=\"Hiroyuki Iida\">Hiroyuki Iida</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_22\">The Game of Synchronized Domineering</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/James_Glenn\" title=\"James Glenn\">James Glenn</a>, <a href=\"/Haw-ren_Fang\" title=\"Haw-ren Fang\">Haw-ren Fang</a>, <a href=\"/Clyde_Kruskal\" title=\"Clyde Kruskal\">Clyde Kruskal</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_23\">A Retrograde Approximation Algorithm for Multi-player Can’t Stop</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Hui_Lu&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Hui Lu (page does not exist)\">Hui Lu</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=ZhengYou_Xia&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"ZhengYou Xia (page does not exist)\">ZhengYou Xia</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_24\">AWT: Aspiration with Timer Search Algorithm in Siguo</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2008</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CG_2008&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/13th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"13th Computer Olympiad\">13th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/WCCC_2008\" title=\"WCCC 2008\">WCCC 2008</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CG_2008&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.geocities.jp/hideki_katoh/13days/6th_day/index.html\">6th. Computer Games Conference 2008 - G